<span class='line-number'>41</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>&lt;%@ page language="java" contentType="text/html; charset=UTF-8" pageEncoding="UTF-8"%&gt;
</span><span class='line'>&lt;%@ page import="java.sql.*"%&gt;
